com.viaoa.object

Class OATypeAhead<F extends OAObject,T extends OAObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.object.OATypeAhead<F,T>

  • public class OATypeAhead<F extends OAObject,T extends OAObject>
extends Object
    Bootstrap TypeAhead support, used by TextField and MultiValueTextField to do searches. For styling, see oajsp.css

    • Method Detail

      • createTypeAhead

        public static OATypeAhead createTypeAhead(String[] values)
        Create a new TA using an array of strings, and update a String property. Example: to update an address.country from a list of countries. String[] countries = ... OATypeAhead ta = OATypeAhead.createTypeAhead(countries, hubAddress, AddressPP.country()); Note: this is treated as a freeform, where user can enter a value that is not in the list.
        Parameters:
        values - array of values to choose from param hubTo hub where AO.propertyName will be updated with selected value from values. param propertyName name of property that is to be updated.
